      <title>泰森食品回吐抛售热潮，鸡肉热销推动利润飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/tyson-foods-beats-earnings-estimates-with-chicken-bonanza</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰森食品公司 (Tyson Foods Inc.) 股价飙升，逆市而上，因为季度收益因鸡肉利润反弹而超过分析师最高预期。]]></description>
